    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate predictive capability for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The six non-assessed factors are appropriate exclusions at MRL 2 given medium model influence and high decision consequence. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied across all five target operating points. The credibility evidence package is accepted as sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
